text: This railway bridge is the primary landmark of the town of Morez, the main town of the canton of the same name Morez is a canton in the département of Jura, France. It belongs to the Arrondissement of Saint-Claude. Since the French canton reorganisation which came into effect in March 2015, the communes of the canton of Morez are:Décret n° 2014-165 du 17 février 2014 portant délimitation des cantons dans le département du Jura * Bellefontaine * Bois-d'Amont * Hauts-de-Bienne * Longchaumois * Morbier * Prémanon * Les Rousses ==References== Category:Cantons of Jura (department)
title: Canton of Morez
